{"sfdt":"NON-DISCLOSURE AGREEMENT

This Non-Disclosure Agreement ("Agreement") is entered into on {{ContractDate}} by and between:

Disclosing Party: {{DisclosingPartyName}}
Address: {{DisclosingPartyAddress}}

Receiving Party: {{ReceivingPartyName}}
Address: {{ReceivingPartyAddress}}

PURPOSE:
The parties wish to explore a business relationship regarding: {{BusinessPurpose}}

CONFIDENTIAL INFORMATION:
For purposes of this Agreement, "Confidential Information" includes all information disclosed by either party, whether written, oral, or visual, including but not limited to:
- Technical data, know-how, research, product plans
- Business information, customer lists, financial information
- Any other information marked or identified as confidential

OBLIGATIONS:
1. The Receiving Party agrees to hold all Confidential Information in strict confidence
2. Not to disclose Confidential Information to any third party without prior written consent
3. To use Confidential Information solely for the purpose of {{BusinessPurpose}}
4. To protect Confidential Information with the same degree of care used for own confidential information

TERM:
This Agreement shall remain in effect for {{ContractTerm}} from the date of execution.

GOVERNING LAW:
This Agreement shall be governed by the laws of {{GoverningLaw}}.

